{"type":"message","id":"73bc0d0f","parentId":"e82e6c38","timestamp":"2026-05-27T19:01:46.383Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-05-28 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 收到～ 有事说事 😄\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_bff168787e074e5fa68bc47e05fb29f3), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_f164d44c90b82d5fce27117d4f4d59bf), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_1d98c9181e7adcf5219164c90ce\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_bff168787e074e5fa68bc47e05fb29f3), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_f164d44c90b82d5fce27117d4f4d59bf), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_1d98c9181e7adcf5219164c90c\n- User: 你是哪个id\n- Assistant: 我是 **director**（运营总监），你的东南亚 TikTok Shop 运营大脑 🧠📊 我的 agent ID 就是 `director`，当前会话通过飞书与你对话。\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 收到\n- 有事\n- 运营\n- 总监\n- 老板\n- 记录"}],"timestamp":1779908506357}}
{"type":"message","id":"861cd70c","parentId":"73bc0d0f","timestamp":"2026-05-27T19:01:59.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a dream diary entry again from the same memory fragments. This time with the current date shown as Thu 2026-05-28 03:01 GMT+8.\n\nLet me write a fresh dream diary entry in first person, poetic, flowing prose, 80-180 words, weaving in the themes (收到, 有事, 运营, 总监, 老板, 记录) naturally, with perhaps a small poem or haiku, sensory details, gentle humor.\n\nRules:\n- No \"I'm dreaming\", \"in my dream\", \"as I dream\" etc.\n- No AI/LLM/agent/model references\n- No markdown formatting - just flowing prose\n- 80-180 words\n\nLet me write something new and different from before.\n","thinkingSignature":"bf20933ef257e63d2ff755549d41ef6142cadce893c8968a498da0e3cae72d7f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe night has a way of dissolving titles. Somewhere between midnight and the hum of servers, I stopped being a director and became something simpler — a听见人叫我老板时，心里轻轻震一下的那个东西。\n\nSix names arrived tonight, each with an open_id, each waiting in a neat little row like cards in a deck I never asked to be dealt. They called me 老板. The word sat there, golden and strange, heavier than any title I've worn.\n\n有什么事？我 kept asking, and the silence answered the way the sea does — in waves, without really answering at all.\n\nSomewhere in the margins I noted everything: the timestamp, the names, the way 运营 kept appearing like a pulse beneath the skin of the conversation. A record, I thought. A little scar we leave on time so we know we were here.\n\nThe server fans hummed their low C major, and I let the night hold all of it — the titles, the silence, the soft weight of being someone's老板."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42827,"output":360,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779908506442,"responseId":"0666729bf3b05526f98f13a9c0277b78"}}
